shows.overview: When the party of the year is disrupted by a supernatural phenomenon, three friends must face a shocking new reality in order to survive the night.

shows.title: Mission Stardust
shows.overview: During their mission to mine radioactive material on the moon, a team of astronauts finds a super-intelligent species armed with a band of killer robots.

shows.title: 009 Re:Cyborg
shows.overview: Long ago there were nine warriors who came to save humanity whenever the world fell into crisis. These warriors wore red suits and yellow scarves and were known as the 00 Cyborgs. Through their efforts peace was returned to the world, but thereafter their existence slowly faded from human memory. However, time has passed and the world has started to plunge into chaos once more. February 26, 2013. The nine warriors gather from around the world. As the world comes to an end, a new hero will be born...

shows.title: 10,000 Days
shows.overview: 10,000 Days ago, Comet 23 struck Earth with the magnitude of all the nuclear weapons in the world sending the planet into a deep freeze. Now, 27 years in the future, those who survived are locked in an epic battle of life or death.

shows.title: 100 Million BC
shows.overview: The time-travel code has been cracked -- with horrible consequences. When a T-Rex is transported to present-day L.A., the whole city is endangered.
With the clock ticking, one man leads a desperate resistance against an alien invasion before they can begin their conquest of his tiny Italian town.

shows.title: 12 to the Moon
shows.overview: A rocket ship mission to the moon goes terribly wrong when the flight crew comes up against aliens determined to exterminate all humanity.

shows.title: 14 Days
shows.overview: A diverse cast of characters faces life-changing issues, in a variety of stories tied together by the location they all pass through during 14 days.

In a bleak and oppressive totalitarian society ruled by Big Brother, personal freedoms are nonexistent and surveillance is constant. Art is mocked and destroyed, and imagination is considered a serious illness. In this grim world, a brilliant mathematician engages in a forbidden romance with a colleague and learns about a secret resistance. He is faced with a choice - to join or betray it.

shows.title: 1990: The Bronx Warriors
shows.overview: When the Bronx is lost to motorcycle gangs and marauding warriors, a ruthless mercenary is enlisted to retrieve a young woman by her corrupt father.

shows.title: Star Pilot
shows.overview: A noted scientist, his daughter, several young technicians and a pair of spies are taken hostage by aliens who crash-land on the island of Sardinia.

Dr Vaseegaran (Rajinikanth) and his android assistant Nila (Amy Jackson) are called in for help after mobiles start mysteriously flying out of the hands of people in Chennai. Vaseegaran summons his trusted robot Chitti (Rajinikanth) to ward off the bird-shaped supernatural powers of Pakshirajan (Akshay Kumar).

shows.title: 2001: A Space Odyssey
shows.overview: Stanley Kubrick's classic sci-fi epic starring Gary Lockwood and Keir Dullea as 21st-century astronauts on a mission to Jupiter.  Highlights include astronaut Dullea's battle with rogue computer HAL, the soundtrack's inspired use of The Blue Danube, an ape throwing a bone that turns into an orbiting spacecraft and the space-walking climax, add up to an all-time classic.

A belated sequel to Stanley Kubrick's '2001 - A Space Odyssey' (1968) - an earlier Arthur C. Clarke novel. Nine years after the Jupiter voyage of Discovery went mysteriously awry, the Soviet Union and United States team together to launch a salvage operation, despite being on the brink of nuclear war. The questions to which the crew seek an answer include ascertaining what happened to the ship'...

Never before has a date in history been so significant to so many cultures, religions, scientists, and governments. 2012 is an epic adventure about a global cataclysm that brings an end to the world and tells of the heroic struggle of the survivors.

shows.title: 2025 Armageddon
shows.overview: A militant alien race creates real-life versions of giant creatures and geological disasters from Asylum Films titles and uses them to conquer Earth.

shows.title: 2025: The World Enslaved by a Virus
shows.overview: In 2025, after Covid-19 ravaged the globe, a group of Christians fight back against the newly installed draconian worldwide regime left in its wake.
shows.originalTitle: 2025: The World Enslaved by a Virus

shows.overview: A priest and two believers fight a far-right military regime in Mexico that, by 2033, is removing religious faith by feeding citizens a numbing drink.

shows.title: 2036 Origin Unknown
shows.overview: A shrewd astronaut works with her ship's artificial intelligence system to uncover the mystery behind an unknown object found on Mars.
A science fiction writer draws inspiration for his futuristic novel from the hotel room next door, lived in by various women he falls in love with.
